<body>
<div id="country3" class="tabcontent">
<div style="width: 740px; border: 1px dashed gray; padding: 10px;  margin:0px auto;">

<h2>Department Issue(CIV)</h2>
<hr />
<span class="title">Screen Overview </span><br />
This screen captures the details of Department Issue(CIV). 
<br />
<hr /><br />
<img src="images/NES_IssueCIVAFF429.jpg" width="725"  /><br /><br />
<hr />
<p>

                                 <span class="title">   Issue Details  </span> <br />

 
 

                   <span class="title"> Civ No: </span> <br />
                    This number is autogenerated by the system.<br />

                   <span class="title">   Issue Date: </span> <br />
                    This text box will show the issue date.<br />

                   <span class="title">  Dept Name :</span> <br />
                    User can write Dept Name in this text box.<br />

                   <span class="title"> Ref No:</span> <br />
                   User can write Ref No in this text box.<br /> 

                    <span class="title">Issued By:</span> <br />
                    User can select Issued By from the drop down box.<br />
                  

                  <span class="title">  SR No.:</span> <br />
                    Auto sequence no. will be generated by the system.<br />

                  <span class="title">  PVMS No.:</span> <br />
                    User can write PVMS No. and press tab. Details of item will be displayed.<br />

                   <span class="title"> Nomenclature:</span> <br />
                    It is description of PVMS No. If PVMS / NIV no. is not entered then type nomenclature initial 2-3 characters, list will be displayed. After nomenclature selection A/U will be displayed.<br />

                 <span class="title">   A/U:</span> <br />
                    Accounting unit of PVMS No will be displayed.<br />

                  <span class="title">  Serial No.:</span> <br />
                    User can select serial no from the list.<br />

                 <span class="title">   Stock in :</span> <br />
                    Write Stock in here.<br />

                 <span class="title">  Qty Issued:</span> <br />
                    Write Qty Issued here.<br />

                 <span class="title">   Next Button:</span> <br />
                    By clicking on the next button next set of rows will be visible like from 9-16 etc.<br />

                  <span class="title">  Submit (Button):</span> <br />
                    By clicking on submit button data will be saved.<br />



</p>

</div>
</body>
